  "title": "Management Development Executive | INJ-B01",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p><ul><li>Support management in daily operations and initiatives</li><li>Assist in coordinating cross-functional projects</li><li>Prepare reports and presentation materials</li><li>Track performance and operational metrics</li><li>Support strategic planning activities</li><li>Participate in rotational assignments across departments and functions to gain broad business exposure</li><li>Gain exposure to leadership decision-making</li><li>Develop foundational management skills</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma and above</li><li>Training will be provided</li><li>Strong learning attitude and adaptability</li><li>Comfortable working with senior stakeholders</li><li>Ambitious and growth-oriented mindset</li></ul><p><strong>EA License Number: 25C2980</strong></p><p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong></p><p>By applying, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data for recruitment purposes in accordance with Singapore’s PDPA. Your application may be considered for this and other suitable roles.</p>",
